{"word":"συμπορεύομαι","slug":"συμπορεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συμπορεύομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-εύσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>συνεπορεύθην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>: <i>to go</i> or <i>journey together</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>τινι</el> <i>with</i> one, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to come together</i>, of the Senate, <b><a href='S:Polybius'>Polyb.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}